00:08:48,180 --> 00:08:52,390
is the law of conservation of mechanical energy.

82
00:08:52,390 --> 00:08:54,990
- You like roller coaster rides, don't you?
- Yes.

83
00:08:54,990 --> 00:08:58,390
The roller coaster demonstrates this law the best

84
