94
00:09:36,370 --> 00:09:40,270
You know that I lied.

95
00:09:40,270 --> 00:09:43,490
Nothing changes by being mad now.

96
00:09:44,370 --> 00:09:46,390
Right now,

97
00:09:48,190 --> 00:09:50,660
I'm just trying to understand

98
00:09:50,660 --> 00:09:52,540
my longtime friend

99
00:09:53,400 --> 00:09:56,120
by putting myself in Ma Hui Yeong kiddo's position.

100
00:09:59,400 --> 00:10:02,490
There must have been a reason for it.

101
00:10:02,490 --> 00:10:04,460
That's the kind of thought I'm having.

102
00:10:08,540 --> 00:10:10,150
Soo Bin.

103
00:10:11,100 --> 00:10:12,900
Hui Yeong.

104
00:10:17,820 --> 00:10:23,570
Just once, I'd like you to think about it really hard

105
00:10:25,030 --> 00:10:31,460
about what feelings you have for me.
Your true feelings.

106
00:10:33,550 --> 00:10:41,210
Whether you did it because you really like me...
or for some other reason.

107
00:10:49,470 --> 00:10:53,030
I thought I was going to suffocate to death.
What's up with you two?

108
00:10:53,030 --> 00:10:57,060
I know. What's up with you guys?

109
00:10:57,060 --> 00:11:00,990
Just, we decided to be friends.

110
00:11:00,990 --> 00:11:02,560
Really?

111
00:11:04,380 --> 00:11:06,030
That's understandable.

112
00:11:06,030 --> 00:11:08,970
It's not easy to break through your mom's close surveillance.

113
00:11:08,970 --> 00:11:12,750
It might be better for now in
order to protect Choi Joon Woo's feelings.

114
00:11:13,940 --> 00:11:17,460
So Ye, did you not make up with Gi Tae?

115
00:11:17,460 --> 00:11:20,330
Hey, how can you forgive that?

116
00:11:20,330 --> 00:11:22,570
When he chooses friendship over love?

117
00:11:22,570 --> 00:11:26,340
What kind of love, what kind of friendship is that?

118
00:11:26,340 --> 00:11:30,870
He was just loyal to his task.
The task of being a butler to Ma Hui Yeong.

119
00:11:35,790 --> 00:11:38,180
What's up with you guys?

120
00:11:38,180 --> 00:11:41,120
You're blatantly excluding me?

121
00:11:41,120 --> 00:11:43,050
Did you just realize that?

122
00:11:43,050 --> 00:11:45,340
Oh... we looked for you but we didn't see you.

123
00:11:45,340 --> 00:11:48,690
You think it's over, right?
Between you and Choi Joon Woo.

124
00:11:50,940 --> 00:11:52,640
So it's true.

125
00:11:54,390 --> 00:11:57,830
Wow, she needs to disappear or something.

126
00:11:59,590 --> 00:12:01,150
It's so yummy.

127
00:12:03,220 --> 00:12:04,890
Ma Hui Yeong did?

128
00:12:04,890 --> 00:12:06,090
Yeah.

129
00:12:07,090 --> 00:12:10,130
- Flabbergasted, right?
- Like a grade-schooler.

130
00:12:11,230 --> 00:12:16,220
Well, it is a ridiculous grade-schooler type of act, but

131
00:12:16,220 --> 00:12:18,980
don't you think it's sort of understandable?

132
00:12:22,790 --> 00:12:26,060
If you lose your mind for a moment—

133
00:12:26,060 --> 00:12:27,740
Hey, Jeong Oh Je.

134
00:12:27,740 --> 00:12:30,380
Well, I'm just saying it is possible to do that.

135
00:12:30,380 --> 00:12:33,120
Talk to Soo Bin soon and make up quickly.

136
00:12:33,120 --> 00:12:36,870
Why make it so complicated and analyze and argue and—

137
00:12:39,690 --> 00:12:42,470
Yoo Pil Sang! Seriously, Yoo Pil Sang.

138
00:12:46,640 --> 00:12:48,240
Hey, I told you to stop, didn't I?

139
00:12:48,240 --> 00:12:51,380
Pil Sang, Joon Woo has antennas right here.

140
00:12:51,380 --> 00:12:53,010
Let's stop, huh?

141
00:12:53,010 --> 00:12:55,040
Pil Sang.

142
00:12:55,780 --> 00:12:59,260
Please don't do this to me and go to Ro Mi.

143
00:12:59,260 --> 00:13:02,270
- Go and confess.
- Are you nuts?

144
00:13:03,070 --> 00:13:04,470
Do I have a death wish?

145
00:13:04,470 --> 00:13:07,060
Do you want to just die or date Ro Mi?

146
00:13:09,630 --> 00:13:12,500
Have some courage, even if it kills you.

147
00:13:17,290 --> 00:13:19,310
Ro Mi.

148
00:13:19,310 --> 00:13:20,510
I like you.

149
00:13:20,510 --> 00:13:22,310
I know. Don't.

150
00:13:22,310 --> 00:13:23,960
- I want to date you.
- No thanks.

151
00:13:23,960 --> 00:13:26,510
Don't say no unconditionally.

152
00:13:26,510 --> 00:13:30,170
Think about it for a few days,
about how I might be as your boyfriend.

153
00:13:30,170 --> 00:13:31,870
I'm asking you.

154
00:13:32,660 --> 00:13:35,330
Tell me your answer by the school trip.

155
00:13:36,720 --> 00:13:40,040
Wow, to me, Pil Sang is becoming almost cool.

156
00:13:49,330 --> 00:13:52,300
Choi Joon Woo, you did something good.

157
00:13:52,950 --> 00:13:56,270
"Have some courage, even if it kills you."

158
00:13:58,050 --> 00:14:00,870
Like a scene from a drama.

159
00:14:00,870 --> 00:14:02,740
What're you saying?

160
00:14:09,420 --> 00:14:11,240
I'm really...

161
00:14:11,240 --> 00:14:13,840
Who am I to give advice...

162
00:14:15,450 --> 00:14:17,360
when I can't even do it?

163
00:14:18,010 --> 00:14:20,760
So because you're curious about these petty things,

164
00:14:20,760 --> 00:14:23,600
you've been repeatedly contacting the old homeroom teacher?

165
00:14:23,600 --> 00:14:26,580
What are you trying to dig up?

166
00:14:34,690 --> 00:14:39,280
The call cannot be completed.
Please check the number and try again.

167
00:14:44,160 --> 00:14:47,240
Teach, someone is here to see you.

168
00:14:47,240 --> 00:14:48,860
Let them in.

169
00:14:58,770 --> 00:15:00,230
Oh, my...

170
00:15:03,950 --> 00:15:07,580
I was going to return it to you right away,
but I had an interview.

171
00:15:07,580 --> 00:15:11,310
Oh, you must be busy,
but you came all the way here to the school.

172
00:15:11,310 --> 00:15:14,900
- I'm not busy.
- I see.

173
00:15:14,900 --> 00:15:18,690
I guess you did well in the interview. You seem happy.

174
00:15:19,460 --> 00:15:20,820
I failed.

175
00:15:20,820 --> 00:15:22,870
I'm sorry.

176
00:15:22,870 --> 00:15:25,930
Then. Goodbye.

177
00:15:27,520 --> 00:15:29,660
- Wait, Ji Min!
- Yes?

178
00:15:31,820 --> 00:15:32,430
Last time—

179
00:15:32,430 --> 00:15:36,540
Last time when I got you a cab, and now for bringing
your bag today, you want to buy me a drink or a meal.

180
00:15:36,540 --> 00:15:37,980
No, thank you.

181
00:15:37,980 --> 00:15:41,580
- Then—
- Then asking about buying me a cup of tea,

182
00:15:41,580 --> 00:15:42,960
no thank you.

183
00:15:42,960 --> 00:15:46,340
I'm a little busy. Work hard.

184
00:15:46,340 --> 00:15:51,320
It's not about that. It's not about a meal, drink or tea.

185
00:15:55,260 --> 00:15:58,590
"To be honest, I'm kind of attracted to you,
so I want to date you."

186
00:15:58,590 --> 00:16:02,280
If it's something like that, then it's really a no, thank you.

187
00:16:02,280 --> 00:16:04,650
It's not that either.

188
00:16:05,700 --> 00:16:09,790
The thing is, you seemed to be
having a hard time, too, last time.

189
00:16:09,790 --> 00:16:12,470
I wanted to tell you to hang in there.

190
00:16:12,470 --> 00:16:15,350
Everything will turn out well, that's why.
Thanks for the bag.

191
00:16:15,350 --> 00:16:17,560
Get back safely.

192
00:16:19,990 --> 00:16:22,450
Today is not the only day, after all.

193
00:16:23,110 --> 00:16:25,320
Oh, dragonfly!

194
00:16:26,820 --> 00:16:29,200
Good morn...

195
00:16:32,210 --> 00:16:35,400
Now, there's some good news.

196
00:16:36,330 --> 00:16:40,480
The idea that our VP Choi Joon Woo came up with

197
00:16:40,480 --> 00:16:45,020
has been chosen as the main event
of the school trip for the entire grade two class!

198
00:16:45,020 --> 00:16:47,390
Give a big hand!

199
00:16:53,000 --> 00:16:56,590
- But why is he so excited?
- I know.

200
00:16:57,960 --> 00:17:02,070
Since we're doing it anyway, let's prepare for it well

201
00:17:02,070 --> 00:17:06,540
so that we can come in first at games
and in the entire grade. The prize is an air purifier.

202
00:17:06,540 --> 00:17:09,330
Let's do it!

203
00:17:09,330 --> 00:17:12,490
I guess he really wants the air purifier.

204
00:17:14,370 --> 00:17:16,210
Yeah.

205
00:17:29,460 --> 00:17:32,270
I knew it would be like this.

206
00:17:38,800 --> 00:17:42,310
Dad's clothes are missing.

207
00:17:43,490 --> 00:17:47,380
Why would I keep old dirty clothes?
I threw them all away.

208
00:17:47,380 --> 00:17:50,020
But still, I need it.

209
00:17:50,020 --> 00:17:52,090
Then buy something.

210
00:17:52,990 --> 00:17:56,070
How can I buy a part of your memory?

211
00:17:56,070 --> 00:17:59,460
Seriously... I'll go home and check.

212
00:17:59,460 --> 00:18:02,400
Please be that diligent about studying.

213
00:18:02,400 --> 00:18:03,940
Hello?

214
00:18:04,760 --> 00:18:07,720
She hung up, this girl.

215
00:18:07,720 --> 00:18:10,440
- Cosplay for the school trip?
- Yes.

216
00:18:10,440 --> 00:18:14,800
- That idea was suggested by our Joon—
- Seriously, I wonder who came up with that idea.

217
00:18:14,800 --> 00:18:18,140
I'm sure it was by someone who's not into studying.

218
00:18:19,200 --> 00:18:22,780
Why did you make a bento box?
I could have just bought something to eat.

219
00:18:22,780 --> 00:18:24,570
You always buy your food.

220
00:18:24,570 --> 00:18:28,040
Now, since your hands aren't feeling good ...

221
00:18:28,040 --> 00:18:30,200
Thank you.

222
00:18:30,200 --> 00:18:34,050
You must have been very popular
with the boys when you were young.

223
00:18:34,050 --> 00:18:36,100
No way!

224
00:18:36,100 --> 00:18:38,670
I dated just once.

225
00:18:38,670 --> 00:18:41,390
With my son's dad. First love.

226
00:18:41,390 --> 00:18:45,540
Oh, really?
Then you never dated anyone else after you split up?

227
00:18:45,540 --> 00:18:49,590
Well, there were a few, but they weren't so great.

228
00:18:49,590 --> 00:18:52,070
There was no one as good as Joon Woo's dad.

229
00:18:52,070 --> 00:18:53,710
I see.

230
00:18:54,570 --> 00:18:57,390
- I'll enjoy it.
- Yes.

231
00:19:00,010 --> 00:19:02,570
What is your son going to do for the school trip cosplay?

232
00:19:02,570 --> 00:19:05,100
He has his dad's clothes.

233
00:19:05,100 --> 00:19:08,120
I kept some as a memory.

234
00:19:08,120 --> 00:19:10,050
To commemorate?

235
00:19:11,530 --> 00:19:14,460
Your dad wore it on our first date.

236
00:19:14,460 --> 00:19:17,800
He was so cool that day.

237
00:19:19,700 --> 00:19:23,110
Still, they must have been in love, no?

238
00:19:23,110 --> 00:19:26,570
Back then. In that moment...

239
00:19:38,040 --> 00:19:39,720
Mom, can I come in?

240
00:19:39,720 --> 00:19:42,460
Oh, wait a minute.

241
00:19:46,390 --> 00:19:48,920
What is it, son?

242
00:19:54,540 --> 00:19:55,880
What?

243
00:19:55,880 --> 00:19:59,060
Is this the time to be thinking about that kind of stuff?

244
00:19:59,060 --> 00:20:02,540
Soo Bin's in charge of that, right?
So you're trying to help her?

245
00:20:02,540 --> 00:20:08,150
No. I'm the president, so I should help the kids out, that's why.

246
00:20:08,150 --> 00:20:11,420
Go upstairs and study.
I'll get something ready for you.

247
00:20:15,400 --> 00:20:18,220
What if dad finds out?

248
00:20:18,220 --> 00:20:20,800
Yeah, Representative Park.
It's me, Park Geum Ja.

249
00:20:20,800 --> 00:20:24,510
Get a suit prepared for our Hui Yeong.

250
00:20:26,280 --> 00:20:29,430
Oh, good. Retro style.

251
00:20:38,620 --> 00:20:42,280
Are you going on a honeymoon, Yoon Da Huin?

252
00:20:43,550 --> 00:20:46,340
- Oh, you're pretty.
- Ro Mi, today you are pretty.

253
00:20:46,340 --> 00:20:49,200
