What's up with everyone?

255
00:20:52,790 --> 00:20:56,670
Hey, good morning, everyone.

256
00:20:56,670 --> 00:21:00,390
- Is everyone here? VP and President, please take attendance.
- Okay.

257
00:21:08,160 --> 00:21:11,300
Isn't that Jo Sang Hoon?

258
00:21:21,550 --> 00:21:23,060
Didn't he go to Singapore?

259
00:21:23,060 --> 00:21:24,620
Hi guys.

260
00:21:24,620 --> 00:21:26,780
Sang Hoon, how are you here?

261
00:21:26,780 --> 00:21:33,510
Hello, Teacher. I wanted to go on the trip, too,
so I quickly came over from Singapore on a duck boat.

262
00:21:33,510 --> 00:21:34,840
What happened?

263
00:21:34,840 --> 00:21:36,880
I'll tell you later.

264
00:21:38,340 --> 00:21:40,450
Guys!

265
00:21:40,450 --> 00:21:43,170
Jo Sang Hoon!
Hey! Jo Sang Hoon!

266
00:21:43,960 --> 00:21:48,990
Then first, let's get on the bus.
Don't get on the wrong bus!

267
00:21:50,460 --> 00:21:53,530
This, this is...

268
00:21:53,530 --> 00:21:55,120
Go away.

269
00:21:58,860 --> 00:22:03,880
Pil Sang, don't pick and just sit. Accept it.

270
00:22:05,120 --> 00:22:07,430
Come on.

271
00:22:09,250 --> 00:22:10,760
Joon Woo.

272
00:22:10,760 --> 00:22:12,820
Sit here.

273
00:22:12,820 --> 00:22:15,640
That, that fox.

274
00:22:21,360 --> 00:22:23,080
I'll sit in the back.

275
00:22:28,190 --> 00:22:32,550
Looky here.
You've lost all your fears, huh?

276
00:22:32,550 --> 00:22:35,130
- Go past me.
- Hurry up!

277
00:22:35,130 --> 00:22:37,660
Please.

278
00:22:41,200 --> 00:22:43,800
I wonder when we'll start going.

279
00:22:46,150 --> 00:22:48,420
What? So Jo Sang Hoon didn't transfer then?

280
00:22:48,420 --> 00:22:50,720
- His transfer papers weren't even submitted.
- Really?

281
00:22:50,720 --> 00:22:53,950
It's true. You're right.

282
00:22:59,240 --> 00:23:05,050
How exciting, how exciting, so exciting!
Let's go!

283
00:23:05,050 --> 00:23:07,030
The bus is getting close.

284
00:23:12,070 --> 00:23:13,990
Yeah!

285
00:23:13,990 --> 00:23:15,160
Let's go!

286
00:23:15,160 --> 00:23:17,480
Let's go!

287
00:23:17,480 --> 00:23:19,240
Sorry.

288
00:23:22,160 --> 00:23:25,450
I didn't eat breakfast.

289
00:23:25,450 --> 00:23:27,210
Oh, I have something to eat.

290
00:23:27,210 --> 00:23:29,730
Really? Let's eat.

291
00:23:30,880 --> 00:23:32,450
It's so cute!

292
00:23:32,450 --> 00:23:34,520
How were they made?

293
00:23:34,520 --> 00:23:38,650
What is this? What is it?
What, what?

294
00:23:38,650 --> 00:23:40,770
Joon Woo, what is it? Me too.

295
00:23:40,770 --> 00:23:44,090
Yeah, here. Ro Mi, take one.

296
00:23:44,090 --> 00:23:46,270
Oh, me too. Huh?

297
00:23:46,270 --> 00:23:49,030
Why are they the same?

298
00:23:49,030 --> 00:23:50,160
It's the same.

299
00:23:50,160 --> 00:23:51,820
Huh?

300
00:23:56,470 --> 00:23:58,140
Take this.

301
00:23:58,140 --> 00:23:58,940
What is it?

302
00:23:58,940 --> 00:24:00,600
My part-time driver brought it for you.

303
00:24:00,600 --> 00:24:02,380
Thank you.

304
00:24:04,240 --> 00:24:07,010
Hey, this one looks good.

305
00:24:07,010 --> 00:24:10,760
Eat this with your friends.
I made it yesterday.

306
00:24:10,760 --> 00:24:12,470
It's been a while since the last time you made this.

307
00:24:12,470 --> 00:24:14,300
Thank you.

308
00:24:26,950 --> 00:24:29,620
VP and the President, take care of them.

309
00:24:29,620 --> 00:24:32,600
- Go this way.
- I don't want to.

310
00:24:38,400 --> 00:24:42,440
So this is where we're staying.

311
00:25:06,740 --> 00:25:08,430
You came.

312
00:25:08,430 --> 00:25:12,180
Don't go overboard.
I didn't come because of what you said.

313
00:25:12,910 --> 00:25:15,130
Ridiculous punk.

314
00:25:24,460 --> 00:25:27,120
Wow, it's so nice!

315
00:25:29,790 --> 00:25:30,770
Wow.

316
00:25:30,770 --> 00:25:33,240
It's not all that.

317
00:25:37,440 --> 00:25:39,700
When will you wear all that?

318
00:25:39,700 --> 00:25:42,320
I can wear them all.

319
00:25:43,900 --> 00:25:46,640
Just make up.

320
00:25:46,640 --> 00:25:49,220
He was walking on eggshells around you.

321
00:25:49,220 --> 00:25:50,480
You should, if anything.

322
00:25:50,480 --> 00:25:53,140
I didn't fight with him.

323
00:25:54,180 --> 00:25:55,540
I didn't either.

324
00:25:55,540 --> 00:25:58,840
Class 3, please come to the auditorium.

325
00:25:58,840 --> 00:26:01,570
Begin!

326
00:26:03,590 --> 00:26:06,050
Five people!

327
00:26:06,050 --> 00:26:07,580
Five people! Five people!

328
00:26:07,580 --> 00:26:09,670
Oh!

329
00:26:09,670 --> 00:26:13,260
♬ For many of my days ♬

330
00:26:13,260 --> 00:26:14,580
♬ I wish you would stay ♬

331
00:26:14,580 --> 00:26:16,800
We lived!

332
00:26:16,800 --> 00:26:21,910
♬ Even if the day is not significant ♬

333
00:26:21,910 --> 00:26:26,360
♬ You, who soothed my feelings ♬

334
00:26:26,360 --> 00:26:30,680
♬ and told me it's all rignt, ♬

335
00:26:30,680 --> 00:26:33,520
♬ I really need you ♬

336
00:26:33,520 --> 00:26:35,560
Begin!

337
00:26:35,560 --> 00:26:41,230
♬ As much as the day's ending will not be sad ♬

338
00:26:41,230 --> 00:26:48,650
♬ Today I will say you are appreciated ♬

339
00:27:02,100 --> 00:27:03,890
Two people!

340
00:27:03,890 --> 00:27:06,090
Two people, two people!

341
00:27:22,900 --> 00:27:25,950
If you're by yourself, get out.

342
00:27:26,730 --> 00:27:30,470
If you're by yourself, get out!

343
00:27:30,470 --> 00:27:32,860
Yes.

344
00:27:32,860 --> 00:27:34,960
What is this?

345
00:27:37,210 --> 00:27:38,940
Hi.

346
00:27:46,340 --> 00:27:48,350
Da Huin.

347
00:27:48,350 --> 00:27:51,440
You were here.
I looked for you everywhere.

348
00:27:51,440 --> 00:27:54,110
Jeong Oh Je. Give this to me.

349
00:27:54,110 --> 00:27:56,340
It's totally my style.

350
00:28:00,220 --> 00:28:03,400
How do you go around flirting with every single boy here?

351
00:28:03,400 --> 00:28:04,620
What?

352
00:28:04,620 --> 00:28:06,690
Da Huin.

353
00:28:11,650 --> 00:28:12,860
Did you just hit me?

354
00:28:12,860 --> 00:28:15,280
No, I was just—

355
00:28:15,280 --> 00:28:17,090
Hey, Hwang Ro Mi!

356
00:28:17,090 --> 00:28:19,390
This wench!

357
00:28:23,470 --> 00:28:26,120
What's the matter?

358
00:28:27,270 --> 00:28:29,390
Ro Mi!

359
00:28:34,050 --> 00:28:36,100
Don't!

360
00:28:38,140 --> 00:28:39,890
Wait, hold up!

361
00:28:39,890 --> 00:28:42,250
Hit me instead! Ow!

362
00:28:45,580 --> 00:28:47,920
Stop!

363
00:28:48,540 --> 00:28:50,570
Get lost!

364
00:29:05,420 --> 00:29:08,160
Guys, let's go have dinner.

365
00:29:08,160 --> 00:29:09,150
I don't want to.

366
00:29:09,150 --> 00:29:11,000
I don't want to.

367
00:29:17,120 --> 00:29:19,750
Da Huin, open the door.

368
00:29:20,790 --> 00:29:22,750
It's Oh Je.

369
00:29:26,610 --> 00:29:28,530
Don't open it.

370
00:29:30,200 --> 00:29:32,230
Da Huin.

371
00:29:33,400 --> 00:29:36,740
Da Huin. I know you're in there.

372
00:29:36,740 --> 00:29:40,690
What if he gets caught for being at the girls' dorm?

373
00:29:48,520 --> 00:29:50,240
Da Huin.

374
00:29:50,240 --> 00:29:52,160
Excuse me.

375
00:29:54,880 --> 00:29:56,810
So Ye.

376
00:30:14,930 --> 00:30:18,100
Soo Bin, should we go have dinner?

377
00:30:21,220 --> 00:30:23,010
I'll carry it now.

378
00:30:23,010 --> 00:30:25,570
You don't have to come tomorrow.
I'm going on a business trip to Japan.

379
00:30:25,570 --> 00:30:28,320
Okay, travel safely.

380
00:30:30,920 --> 00:30:32,740
Soo Bin's mom.

381
00:30:35,710 --> 00:30:36,810
Why are you here?

382
00:30:36,810 --> 00:30:39,280
I know Soo Bin went on a school trip.

383
00:30:39,280 --> 00:30:41,610
What kind of woman is always the same no matter when?

384
00:30:41,610 --> 00:30:45,390
Just cold and stiff. Seriously.

385
00:30:46,810 --> 00:30:48,690
The keys!

386
00:30:57,100 --> 00:30:59,220
Hello!

387
00:30:59,220 --> 00:31:00,970
Hi!

388
00:31:02,940 --> 00:31:06,410
I don't want a divorce. I won't.
How many times do I have to tell you?

389
00:31:06,410 --> 00:31:11,220
You know how important this time is for Soo Bin.
Are you nuts?

390
00:31:11,220 --> 00:31:13,120
Soo Bin will understand.

391
00:31:13,120 --> 00:31:17,330
If I'm to go to the US next year,
I have to sort out our papers.

392
00:31:17,330 --> 00:31:20,060
Why? Because you have to marry that wench?

393
00:31:20,060 --> 00:31:23,450
Song Hui, let's stop criticizing now.

394
00:31:23,450 --> 00:31:27,520
Pretending we're happy parents in front of Soo Bin,
acting like we're a loving couple in front of others.

395
00:31:27,520 --> 00:31:28,920
I don't like doing that either.

396
00:31:28,920 --> 00:31:31,500
Do you think I want to put on a show?

397
00:31:31,500 --> 00:31:33,590
But a divorce isn't possible.

398
00:31:33,590 --> 00:31:37,720
Until Soo Bin gets into college, I can't.

399
00:31:37,720 --> 00:31:40,550
Stop using her as an excuse.

400
00:31:40,550 --> 00:31:43,750
- Just beg me not to break up, if anything.
- What?

401
00:31:44,810 --> 00:31:49,480
Pretending you're the best, like you're cool,

402
00:31:49,480 --> 00:31:51,080
I'm sick and tired of it, really.

403
00:31:51,080 --> 00:31:54,310
Beg for what? You think I still like you?

404
00:31:54,310 --> 00:31:58,020
Now that you're living comfortably after the money
I earned to give us a good life?

405
00:31:58,020 --> 00:32:00,350
You're the one who needs to... Seriously!

406
00:32:00,350 --> 00:32:03,340
You're the one who should be more honest!

407
00:32:03,340 --> 00:32:07,690
It's much nicer to live with a woman
who's less smart and less great.

408
00:32:07,690 --> 00:32:11,170
So that's why you're leaving.
Be honest and say that. Please.

409
00:32:11,170 --> 00:32:14,010
You know, so why ask? Huh?

410
00:32:14,010 --> 00:32:18,200
Decide by next week.
If not, I'll sue you.

411
00:32:51,220 --> 00:32:53,690
Why did you come?

412
00:32:56,250 --> 00:32:59,010
Go in, Soo Bin's mom.

413
00:33:01,280 --> 00:33:03,950
I'll do it.

414
00:33:03,950 --> 00:33:07,850
Gwon Da Huin.
You're mistaken.

415
00:33:07,850 --> 00:33:09,670
I have no interest in Ro Mi.

416
00:33:09,670 --> 00:33:11,650
Then why did you look at her?

417
00:33:11,650 --> 00:33:13,590
I didn't.

418
00:33:13,590 --> 00:33:17,360
That hat earlier, she just took it from me.

419
00:33:17,360 --> 00:33:19,620
She's always doing whatever she wants.

420
00:33:19,620 --> 00:33:24,600
I'm being honest. I'm not interested in any other girl.

421
00:33:24,600 --> 00:33:25,950
I'm the closest with you.

422
00:33:25,950 --> 00:33:28,000
Really?

423
00:33:29,900 --> 00:33:31,450
Then do you like me the best?

424
00:33:31,450 --> 00:33:34,250
- Huh?
- I'm asking if you like me.

425
00:33:38,140 --> 00:33:40,090
Oh, Teach! Teach.

426
00:33:42,710 --> 00:33:44,970
We nearly got in trouble.

427
00:33:50,780 --> 00:33:51,770
Da Huin.

428
00:33:51,770 --> 00:33:55,830
Cute. I love you, Oh Je.

429
00:33:57,790 --> 00:34:00,330
I know how lacking I am.

430
00:34:00,330 --> 00:34:03,960
Following around Ma Hui Yeong
and watching my every move with him.

431
00:34:03,960 --> 00:34:07,560
Mistaking that I could be just like him.

432
00:34:08,650 --> 00:34:09,710
Gi Tae.

433
00:34:09,710 --> 00:34:12,190
I am lacking,

434
00:34:12,190 --> 00:34:18,130
really lacking, so I have no right to like you, but I do.

435
00:34:19,110 --> 00:34:21,160
I really like you.

436
00:34:21,160 --> 00:34:23,250
I really like you, So Ye.

437
00:34:23,250 --> 00:34:27,410
But since you're being this cold to me,

438
00:34:28,290 --> 00:34:30,780
it's so hard for me, So Ye.

439
00:34:32,500 --> 00:34:36,390
Stand up. I said stand up.

440
00:34:40,200 --> 00:34:42,600
I won't do it, So Ye.

441
00:34:44,180 --> 00:34:45,360
According to each class,

442
00:34:45,360 --> 00:34:46,920
sort out the items properly!

443
00:34:46,920 --> 00:34:48,560
Class one!

444
00:34:48,560 --> 00:34:50,400
That's right.

445
00:34:52,780 --> 00:34:54,420
Ma Hui Yeong.

446
00:34:55,130 --> 00:34:58,400
You're disappointed that I came back, right?

447
00:34:58,400 --> 00:34:59,430
Whatever.

448
00:34:59,430 --> 00:35:04,170
That can't be.
You must be really scared.

449
00:35:05,900 --> 00:35:07,580
What?

450
00:35:08,930 --> 00:35:11,060
I'm kidding.

451
00:35:11,060 --> 00:35:13,100
Seriously, I'm so thankful to your father.

452
00:35:13,100 --> 00:35:17,450
He promoted my dad and let me continue to stay on here.

453
00:35:17,450 --> 00:35:21,750
He's an angel.
How can I pay him back?

454
00:35:24,280 --> 00:35:27,470
Let's do well, friend.
Take good care of me.

455
00:35:31,520 --> 00:35:33,330
Let's go.

456
00:35:38,330 --> 00:35:41,960
Are you happy? Satisfied?

457
00:35:46,810 --> 00:35:49,120
Would you be if you were me?

458
00:35:49,120 --> 00:35:51,260
It's hard for Soo Bin...

459
00:36:12,780 --> 00:36:14,590
Hui Yeong.

460
00:36:15,720 --> 00:36:17,880
I'll help you.

461
00:36:17,880 --> 00:36:20,460
You should have called me.

462
00:36:20,460 --> 00:36:22,260
It's fine.

463
00:36:39,950 --> 00:36:41,640
Come on!

464
00:36:43,230 --> 00:36:45,250
Oh!

465
00:36:46,560 --> 00:36:48,940
We have a summer home in Santa Monica.

466
00:36:48,940 --> 00:36:50,430
Santa Monica? As expected.

467
00:36:50,430 --> 00:36:53,100
It reminds me of having a barbecue party in the garden there.

468
00:36:53,100 --> 00:36:57,420
You only ran your mouth there at the
Santa Monica summer home, too, didn't you?

469
00:36:57,420 --> 00:37:00,060
Without lifting a finger?

470
00:37:01,870 --> 00:37:04,720
Hwang Ro Mi, it turned out you're a total liar!

471
00:37:04,720 --> 00:37:08,030
What? Your dad is the director of Jae Yeong Hospital?

472
00:37:09,890 --> 00:37:11,620
Hey, come here.

473
00:37:11,620 --> 00:37:16,060
Your father is the driver of that hospital's head!
How dare you pretend?

474
00:37:16,060 --> 00:37:19,080
All of our team's moms nearly got fooled!

475
00:37:19,080 --> 00:37:22,810
I knew it. You always made excuses
whenever there was a meeting with the parents.

476
00:37:22,810 --> 00:37:25,450
You lied about your mom being a professor, too, didn't you?

477
00:37:25,450 --> 00:37:27,990
Pil Sang, it's your chance.
Come on, go over there!

478
00:37:29,230 --> 00:37:31,940
It's because it might embarrass Ro Mi.

479
00:37:32,780 --> 00:37:34,970
What are you doing in our class?
Talk about it later.

480
00:37:34,970 --> 00:37:39,010
- Let go. It's ridiculous when her dad's not even a doctor.
- Hey!

481
00:37:40,460 --> 00:37:41,950
- He is a doctor.
- What?

482
00:37:41,950 --> 00:37:46,400
My mom got treated by her father when she was sick last time.

483
00:37:46,400 --> 00:37:49,130
How dare you make a scene after hearing crappy rumors?

484
00:37:49,130 --> 00:37:52,300
Kwon Da Huin, did I ask you to help?

485
00:37:52,300 --> 00:37:55,070
Fine, my dad's not a hospital director.

486
00:37:55,070 --> 00:37:58,800
I lied a little. So what?

487
00:37:58,800 --> 00:38:02,130
That I'm pretty and good in school, too,
just like her hospital director father,

488
00:38:02,130 --> 00:38:05,610
saying that they're dying from envy, who said that?

489
00:38:05,610 --> 00:38:06,420
Wasn't it you?

490
00:38:06,420 --> 00:38:07,740
So who told you to lie?

491
00:38:07,740 --> 00:38:12,090
Who told you to get fooled? It's the mistake
of the wench who got fooled.

492
00:38:13,420 --> 00:38:15,410
Hwang Ro Mi!

493
00:38:15,410 --> 00:38:17,350
Don't come.

494
00:38:28,890 --> 00:38:32,810
You're up.
Have some porridge.

495
00:38:34,220 --> 00:38:36,760
If you leave it, I'll eat it later.

496
00:38:36,760 --> 00:38:38,300
- Okay.
- Thank you.

497
00:38:44,710 --> 00:38:46,750
Then I'll leave.

498
00:38:46,750 --> 00:38:48,390
Okay.

499
00:38:50,440 --> 00:38:52,190
Yeon Woo.

500
00:38:56,190 --> 00:39:01,550
That is... you working for me, let's end it after today.

501
00:39:01,550 --> 00:39:03,410
But your hand isn't even all healed yet.

502
00:39:03,410 --> 00:39:06,580
I'll come for a few days more after
you return from your business trip.

503
00:39:06,580 --> 00:39:08,800
I'll just take a cab.

504
00:39:08,800 --> 00:39:10,630
I'm a little embarrassed to see you now.

505
00:39:10,630 --> 00:39:12,160
What do you mean?

506
00:39:12,160 --> 00:39:14,450
Let's just do that.

507
00:39:20,160 --> 00:39:23,280
Now, next.

508
00:39:25,670 --> 00:39:29,780
We'll start the truth hearing!

509
00:39:31,430 --> 00:39:33,430
Then... drum roll.

510
00:39:37,420 --> 00:39:40,190
Gi Tae Lee!

511
00:39:41,680 --> 00:39:43,480
Take a seat.

512
00:39:46,060 --> 00:39:48,400
Just throw your questions out, okay?

513
00:39:48,400 --> 00:39:49,510
Then...

514
00:39:49,510 --> 00:39:52,710
before dinner, you were absent for a moment.

515
00:39:52,710 --> 00:39:54,660
Where did you go?

516
00:39:54,660 --> 00:39:57,280
I went to speak to So Ye.

517
00:39:59,700 --> 00:40:03,600
What did you talk about with So Ye?

518
00:40:04,920 --> 00:40:07,490
I made a lot of mistakes, so...

519
00:40:17,400 --> 00:40:20,060
What are you doing after coming all the way here?
Let's play together.

520
00:40:20,060 --> 00:40:22,330
I'm okay. Call me when you need me.

521
00:40:22,330 --> 00:40:24,350
